Kerry Howard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerry_Howard 0 Kerry Elizabeth Howard (born 24 March 1982) is an English actress. She played Laura in the BBC Three comedy series Him Her and Leanne in Witless. She also appears in BBC Three "Feed My Funny" comedy sketches with Lu Corfield and acts as courtroom clerk in Judge Romesh. Kerry_Elizabeth_Howard ( born 24_March_1982 ) is an_English_actress .
